comments: Coffey (LAC) maintains a legal guarding position on Beal (WAS) during the drive. Beal does not bring two hands to the ball to stop his dribble.
Hartenstein (LAC) legally contests and cleanly blocks Beal's (WAS) jump shot attempt.
Harrell (LAC) cleanly blocks Coffey's (LAC) driving shot attempt prior to the ball touching the backboard.
Hartenstein (LAC) avoids any contact with Beal's (WAS) arm as Beal bobbles the ball upon receiving the pass.
Kennard (LAC) establishes himself in Harrell's (WAS) path and marginal contact occurs as he mutually engages and disengages with Dinwiddie (WAS) during the pick.
Dinwiddie (WAS) moves alongside of Hartenstein (LAC) and absorbs the marginal contact during the driving shot attempt.
Kuzma (WAS) makes clean hand on ball contact to dislodge the rebound from Mann (LAC).
Kennard (LAC) reaches in and makes contact with Caldwell-Pope's (WAS) arm, which affects his driving shot attempt.
Harrell (WAS) extends his arm around Mann's (LAC) body and makes contact with his arm, which affects his SQBR during the transition play up the court.
Mann (LAC) avoids contact with Kuzma's (WAS) arm during his steal attempt in the backcourt.
Kuzma (WAS) lifts and re-plants his pivot foot prior to passing the ball.
Upon Dinwiddie (WAS) receiving and bobbling the pass, Scrubb (LAC) makes clean ball contact during his steal attempt.
Winslow (LAC) wraps his arms around Harrell's (WAS) body and makes contact with his arm, which affects his play at the basket.
Kuzma (WAS) avoids contact with Coffey's (LAC) arm on his dislodge attempt during the play at the basket.
Kispert (WAS) establishes himself in a screening position in Coffey's (LAC) path and absorbs the contact during the screen.
Scrubb (LAC) commits a take foul on Kuzma (WAS).
Winslow (LAC) does not release the inbound within 5 seconds.
Kuzma (WAS) does not release the inbounds pass within 5 seconds.
Dinwiddie (WAS) brushes Kennard's (LAC) body and marginal contact occurs, which does not affect his SQBR.

Beal (WAS) places two hands on Kennard's (LAC) body and makes contact with his arm, prior to the start of his upward shooting motion. A personal foul should be assessed and the basket should not count.

call_type: Turnover:  Out of Bounds - Bad Pass Turn
comments: Harrell (WAS) can't cleanly control Kuzma's (WAS) full court pass and the ball goes out of bounds. Possession is correctly awarded to the Clippers.
Beal (WAS) briefly grasps Coffey's (LAC) arm and marginal contact occurs as they disengage, which does not affect his ability to get to the inbounds pass.
